response.overview: Distinguished musicians Ramkrishna Paul, Uday Dey and Partha Paul perform some of the most popular Indian songs of all time in this entertaining compilation of tunes. The instrumental collection -- featuring Ramkrishna on violin, Uday on flute and Partha on keyboards -- includes "Achey Dukho Achey Mrithyu," "Alcash Bhora Surja Tara," "Din Guli More Sonar Khancha" and "Ae ki Labanya Purno Pran," among others.
response.title: Rabindrasangeet Instrumental
